commit.message:
[PATCH][GCC][DOC] Remove obsolete arm and aarch64 CPU names from invoke.texi

gcc/ChangeLog:

2018-11-28  Sam Tebbs  <sam.tebbs@arm.com>

	* doc/invoke.texi (-mtune=): Remove obsolete CPU names.

From-SVN: r266549
